                    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">We work around your fitness classes, golf games, club activities, and travel schedules to provide convenient service.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
                    <div style="background: #ff8057; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem;">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Guest-Ready Always</h4>
                    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Keeping your home ready for family visits, friends, and the active social life that makes OTOW special.</p>
                </div>
